claim.claim-text:
A force sensor that detects external force, the force sensor comprising:
a sheath (2);
a pressure member (1) configured to be provided on the sheath;
sensor means configured to detect force applied to the pressure member; and
slip ring means configured to supply power or transmit signals through a contact between a rotating body and a stationary body,
wherein the sensor means and the slip ring means are stored in the sheath, and power is supplied or signals are transmitted between the slip ring unit and the sensor unit.
